  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nAt the moment we're using `BitAnd` (i.e. `&`) as an operator for computing the union of two bitfields, despite the underlying operation being more like a `BitOr` (i.e. `|`). We should change to using `BitOr` for union, and possibly `BitAnd` for intersection.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nChange `BitOr` to `BitAnd`, fix all usage sites (looks like not many: I've already done this on my operation-pool branch)\r\n",
